About the revised map.

294
00:37:41,829 --> 00:37:46,513
If you would like to visit more than one breakout room, you may switch between rooms at any point.

295
00:37:47,133 --> 00:37:52,637
You will have to leave that room, come to the main room, and then rejoin with a different breakout room.

296
