So we're going to be in breakout rooms for 40 minutes.

308
00:38:52,895 --> 00:39:02,823
So, even though the slide says 715, we will stay in there until 720 and then at 720, you'll be moved back to the main room and we will do Q and a.

309
00:39:04,655 --> 00:39:15,842
If you do have any difficulty selecting a breakout room to join, please just write in the chat what room you want to join and we can move you into that room.

